<br>
100pp is not that much. i carry around 4 quintessence of knowledge, for times when i may find myself in a group with no porter. rather than leave melee stranded i can give them a talisman so they can port themselves out.<br>
<br>
im glad i have the spell, but i do not think it should be turned into a tl or a port. there is a reason our offense is generally more flexible than wizards and that is because they have better non offensive abilities than we do.<br>
<br>
really people, think before you speak. its clear this is designed to be a situational spell. not every spell you have should be useful all the time. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=noonievioletskies>NoonieVioletskies</A> at: 12/14/02 7:38:50 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=khalendor>Khalendor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 179<br> <font color=#333333>(12/14/02 7:57:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=163.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Talisman of Return - Remove the reagent please.</span><hr size=1> Just because some people don't find the Talisman useful, doesn't mean they aren't thinking before they speak. <p>Khalendor Dayze</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kathodos>Kathodos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 319<br> <font color=#333333>(12/17/02 5:10:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=163.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.battle.net/war3/images/human/units/portraits/waterelement.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Talisman of Return - Remove the reagent please.</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Noonie:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> 100pp is not that much. i carry around 4 quintessence of knowledge, for times when i may find m