<br>
Also, by your example, you have to spend 400pp to be a contender for that group spot, rather than the Wizard/Druid.  I don't think it's justifiable that Magicians should have to buy their way into groups.  Remember, because of the cost, and the extreme limited use (if there is one) of this spell, noone other than the Magician will know about the reagent nor carry it.<br>
<br>
The claims haven't been to make the spell instant cast, no reagent, unlimited charges.  We're not after an unbalancing ability, or to become the be all and end all of EQ transport.<br>
<br>
Merely reduce the reagent so that it's not something that requires a class specific tradeskill which is unavailable to the Magician class, and preferably something that is commonly carried and not extremely expensive.  With a 30 second cast, and single charge, it's going to remain situational at best.<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Noonie:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> really people, think before you speak. its clear this is designed to be a situational spell. not every spell you have should be useful all the time.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->So many Magicians have responded with constructive suggestions on how to improve a spell they've never had a use for, and you accuse them of not thinking.  Perhaps 400pp per group isn't a lot to you Noonie, but it's a heck of a lot to some of us, especially those in smaller guilds or unguilded.  So far this &quot;situationally usefull spell&quot; has yet to find a use. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=59365" target="top">Kathodos</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Battle Cleric of Tunare - Tholuxe Paells<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=279732" target="top">Kantreach</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Arch Mage Antagonist - Tholuxe Paells</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kathodos>Kathodos</A> at: 12/17/02 5:13:32 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=khalendor>Khalendor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 180<br> <font color=#333333>(12/17/02 6:24:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=163.topic&inde