As with anyone else here, I am only offering my opinion on this spell.  It would be nice if the reagent were cheaper, but at this level 100pp is nothing.  Nonetheless, I carry 2 stacks of these with me, and it is my pleasure to offer them to guildies in need.  <br>
Who hasn't paid 100pp for one of the KEI dealers in Nexus bazaar?  <br>
<br>
I'm not flaming anyone by any means, only offering a different view, so please don't do it either.  Have a happy day!<br>
