<br>
When I first heard of the spell, I was excited cause I am bound in PoM. I was hoping it'd give me a chance to get to PoK when needed, or so I could at least mem gate again.<br>
<br>
if it required a no fail combine that cost 20-50pp that you combine in an alchemy bag, it'd be worth using.<br>
<br>
if it required a 200 trivial alchemy combine that cost 100pp but was insta-cast, it'd be good for an escape spell.<br>
<br>
if it cost portal fragments just so you couldn't use it when on CR, it'd be at least useful as a second bind point.<br>
<br>
as it is now, it's just too expensive and illogical to be practical for anything. <br>
<br>
